        "name": "Cutting Eye",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "**Sin:** envy  \n  \nYour eyes open enviously, stealing the power of an opponent for yourself. You are not off-guard to the attacker or spellcaster until the beginning of your next turn. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your AC against the triggering attack or a +2 circumstance bonus to the triggering save.",
